results.wikipedia_summary: An aracari or araçari (US /ˌɑːrəˈsɑːri/ AHR-ə-SAHR-ee,UK /ˌɑrəˈsɑːri/ ARR-ə-SAHR-ee or /ˌɑrəˈkɑːri/ ARR-ə-KAHR-ee) is any of the medium-sized toucans that, together with the Saffron Toucanet, make up the genus Pteroglossus.
